-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_msl_division
-- AS
SELECT
[KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO]
,[FUNC_TOTAL]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_msl_division.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) with (
         [KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO] VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[FUNC_TOTAL] VARCHAR(10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) as ROW
